WOlfblade::

She heard Malice on the com and her instincts told her trouble was
brewing. She looked at Silence. "Come with us back to base. It will be
safer there than out in the woods with Preds roaming around at night."
She turned to Malice with worry in her optics. "Fill me in as we go
along."

Silence::
She nodded and transformed into owl mode and started going skyward.
"I'll follow you." she said in a soft and delicate voice.

WOlfblade::
She looked at Malice. "OK, let get going. And please, tell me what was
 going on with the message from Kup?"


--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, robert riley <bustercross365@y...> wrote:
> Malice:
>  
> He thought he heard Kup wrong, but each time he replayed the
message, it still said that his sister and the one she loved was back
and alright.  He fought the outburst he wanted to give, and simply smlied.
>  
> "Thanks Kup, I'll see them after we get back."
>  
> He closed the comm and turned back to Wolfblade and Silence, waiting
for what they were to do here.
>
